  <sect1 id="top">
    <para>Other OSs have <ulink 
	url="http://www.linux.org/docs/howto.html">HowTo</ulink>s,
      we now have a WhereTo! The files here should help you in
      setting up your ICBM (InterContinental Ballistic
      Missile) properly if you should feel the need to nuke a
      <ulink url="../../people/">NetBSD developer</ulink> or 
      two. :-)</para>

